title: Ep. 907 Another Liberal Conspiracy Theory Collapses
description:
In this episode I address the latest, incredible, job numbers while debunking liberal claims that this is due to Obama’s economic policies. I also address the complete collapse of a prominent liberal conspiracy theory about Donald Trump. 
 
News Picks:
Incredible job numbers were just posted.
 
A deported child molester was just apprehended at the border.
 
Adam Schiff gets destroyed, again!
 
Don Trump Jr. fights back against shady Adam Schiff.
 
This key Spygate figure is giving up some of the players. 
 
President Trump makes bold picks for the liberal Ninth Circuit Court of Appeals.
